headline: Unpacking Q3 Earnings: Byrna (NASDAQ:BYRN) In The Context Of Other Aerospace and Defense Stocks
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Byrna (NASDAQ:BYRN) and the best and worst performers in the aerospace and defense industry.
